snippet.title: Mega Man X2 Alpha: 100% No Damage Completion Run
snippet.description:
Mega Man X2 Alpha is a Hard Mode MOD created by "Myself Thethird"
Alpha is a different project from Hard Type so there's an error in the mmx2 title.
You can follow the progress of Alpha series in the author's channel:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC8lHJjcz43f3cB8bttgO4qg

Stage Timestamps:

01:00 (Intro Stage)
03:05 Wheel Gator
07:55 Overdrive Ostrich
11:57 Bubble Crab
15:05 Flame Stag
18:52 Crystal Snail
23:13 Morph Moth
28:22 Wire Sponge
30:49 Magna Centipede
34:26 Hunter Stage 1 (Violen)
36:53 Hunter Stage 2 (Serges)
39:10 Hunter Stage 3 (Agile)
46:57 Final Stage (Sigma)
